The thumbnail-extraction logic in this project (parsing of the embedded
thumbnails inside .3mf / .gcode / .bgcode files) is a clean-room Swift
re-implementation derived from the design and behavior of ThumbHost3mf's
Objective-C/C sources (Thumbnail3MF, ThumbnailGCode, ThumbnailBinaryGCode,
Unzip3MF, QOIFImageFromData). See ARCHITECTURE.md for details on what was
reused and why.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
